metadata.title: MMNNE 2Pack 90 Degree Up Angled Ethernet LAN RJ45 Male to Female Adapter Shielded Network Patch Connector (Black Up Angled)
features: 90 degree ethernet adapter is more convenient to use RJ45 port to connect network equipment. It can be used in narrow spaces like behind furniture or behind a TV. Avoid continuous plugging and unplugging of network ports,prevent the Ethernet cable from bending and causing damage.
Gold Plated Connector - Gold-plated RJ45 connector ensures a high speed and efficient signal transfer.90 degree compact design, compact shape, space saving.
Safe and Secure -Cat6/ Cat5e / Cat5 Standards RJ45 8P8C Cords.
Ethernet cable extender is perfect for extending your existing ethernet connection to reach a router or video steaming device, and protect the computer network port from constant plug and unplug.

90 Degree Ethernet Adapter has wide range of compatibility, which can connects PC, computer servers, routers, printers, switch boxes, network media players, xBox, NAS, VoIP phones, PoE devices, PS2, PS3, Hub, DSL etc.
